          0,
          "At issue is a suit brought by Texas oil and gas billionaire Kelcy Warren. It accuses former Democratic gubernatorial candidate Beto O‚ÄôRourke of defamation for slamming Warren‚Äôs $1 million donation to Texas Gov. Greg Abbott (R) in 2021."
